        "subject": "ATM-1421 tests: incorporate sanity-pcc into testing",
        "message": "ATM-1421 tests: incorporate sanity-pcc into testing\n\nThe test suite canity-pcc was added to the Lustre test\nsuites with the landing of the PCC feature in Lustre.\n\nThis patch is for test only to make sure that sanity-pcc\npasses in all our test configurations.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly fstype=zfs mdscount=2 mdtcount=4 clientcount=2 osscount=1 ostcount=8 testlist=sanity-pcc\nTest-Parameters: fstype=ldiskfs mdscount=2 mdtcount=4 clientcount=2 osscount=1 ostcount=8 testlist=sanity-pcc\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly fstype=zfs mdscount=1 mdtcount=1 clientcount=2 osscount=1 ostcount=2 testlist=sanity-pcc\nTest-Parameters: fstype=ldiskfs mdscount=1 mdtcount=1 clientcount=2 osscount=1 ostcount=2 testlist=sanity-pcc\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <jnunez@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I094e30f5d3bf5dc1defc4f0cf84ebcb28bc4d500\n"
      },
